Ans: If you would like to register other bank accounts for fund transfer, please visit our branch for processing or please fill in form(the form can be downloaded from the Bankâ€™s website) and send the form to our branch by post for processing.You can register by yourself after login the internet banking if you have registered two-factor authentication service.
